# Application Layer (`packages/application`)

- Use cases orchestrate domain logic; they do not contain framework code
- External systems accessed only through adapter interfaces defined here or in `packages/adapters`
- Authorization policy service called before any data read or write
- Audit events emitted for mutating operations
- Application services are the only entry point for agents and workers to mutate state

## Agent integration

LangGraph tools invoke application services — never database clients directly.
